{"tid":2351635,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"成員確診新冠後毫無消息...EVERGLOW公司處理手法引韓網熱論!","createTime":"2021-01-03T11:33:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T12:40:40.000Z","uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e76a082440661598ee80b86a31ba5923e5588088","tid":2351635,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T11:33:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/01/03/550_1557559_1609651336.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F01%2F03%2F550_1557559_1609651336.webp&h=c6e80525&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3日，一篇關於韓國女子組合EVERGLOW的文章成為了韓網熱帖，吸引了多人討論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/01/03/550_1557557_1609651340.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F01%2F03%2F550_1557557_1609651340.webp&h=4ed62cb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該篇文章標題為「情況嚴重的EVERGLOW」，在文章中，帖主指出，EVERGLOW最後一次上傳Youtube物料的日子是11月28日，成員最後一次上傳Twitter帖文也是在同一天。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/01/03/550_1557558_1609651344.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F01%2F03%2F550_1557558_1609651344.webp&h=6fa50d9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外，EVERGLOW的成員們原本一天會登入一次官咖，但從12月1日起就再無登入過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/01/03/550_1557562_1609651354.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F01%2F03%2F550_1557562_1609651354.webp&h=ac6c447f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據悉，在12月1日，EVERGLOW經紀公司樂華娛樂發出聲明，指成員王怡人的新冠檢測結果為陽性，因住在同一間宿舍的關係，成員金施賢也被檢測為陽性，確診新冠肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n在此之後，樂華就再沒有公告過與EVERGLOW相關的消息，粉絲們連兩位成員是否已經康復都不知道，也不知道成員們到底已經回家，還是仍然住在宿舍。<br />\n<br />\n對此，有網民認為，成員們沒有消息只是因為有成員確診了新冠，公司不好在敏感時期多發消息或讓其他成員活躍地活動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/01/03/550_1557556_1609651332.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F01%2F03%2F550_1557556_1609651332.webp&h=e79b2408&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過，另外也有網民認為公司做法不夠妥當，留言表示：「有點太安靜了，要是粉絲的話感到不安也能理解」、「什麼只是一個月沒消息也可以...想了一下那時是年末和年初，正常也會說新年快樂什麼的，連那些也沒有嗎」、「治癒中的話就應該說治療中...粉絲們不安也是正常的」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n怡人小姐姐。。。"},{"pid":"80ab6795ed471f45d394acb72b7bbfd2bfd92276","tid":2351635,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T11:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef4282e18ff0497ccda09ae73505030555783800","tid":2351635,"uid":80679,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T11:42:48.000Z","msg":"我仲用緊九陽神功幫拖腎恰人小姐姐迫出體內肺炎<br />\n請大家等多幾個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f5860da2eee70d03d810a17bd41b9a35826599","tid":2351635,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T11:47:33.000Z","msg":"小姐姐會無事的..🙏🏻"},{"pid":"603ac52b81d9cfc2c7c79a6fa8e6f1ab485d6e19","tid":2351635,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T11:48:22.000Z","msg":"RAP<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805af3719a69a1887be29e15ee7f3c401d99b536","tid":2351635,"uid":68678,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef4282e18ff0497ccda09ae73505030555783800","tid":2351635,"uid":80679,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T11:42:48.000Z","msg":"我仲用緊九陽神功幫拖腎恰人小姐姐迫出體內肺炎<br />\n請大家等多幾個月<img src=\